text: Gary Hinchley (born 14 November 1968) is an English former footballer who made 27 appearances in the Football League playing as a full back for Darlington in the 1980s and 1990s. He also played non-league football for clubs including Whitby Town and Guisborough Town. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:People from Guisborough Category:Sportspeople from Yorkshire Category:English footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Darlington F.C. players Category:Whitby Town F.C. players Category:Guisborough Town F.C. players Category:English Football League players
